        public boolean isSecretsAdmin(String assembly)
        Checks if team is a Secrets admin for the given assembly. For a team to be Secrets Admin, the following naming conventions are used.
        • Team name should secrets-admin OR
        • Team name should secrets-admin-${AssemblyName}
        Returns:
        true if the team is a Secrets admin for given assembly.
